title: International passengers: Avoid Adelaide Airport in South Australia
text:
International passengers: Avoid Adelaide Airport in South Australia   
Sep 21, 2015 eTN   
Adelaide Airport is the principal airport of Adelaide, South Australia and the fifth busiest airport in Australia. in 2014 the airport handled almost 8 million passengers. 
Currently Adelaide Airport may not be the best choice for tourists or local to arrive from an airport outside Australia. 
Australian customs is on strike. Today is was announced the strike will continue for at least another week.
